reviews.review_text: mono sounding this version sounds mono kinda, i like the other one better, a little more crispier

playing Bird Song Promised Land, Sugaree, MAMU and Bird Song* are spot on first set. Additionally, this is the PITB that precedes the best one ever and doesn't disappoint. Bird Songs of the second half of '72 are phenomenal. Dark Star>Dew is certainly thoughtful.
